reviews.text: A renovated walking street full of higher end shops and western restaurants.  Some decorations along the street for photo shooting.  Residential blocks were well managed.  Shops and food stores not so expensive were located in the same area.

One of the happening place in wanchai area, vibes of this place I always love. You can have places such as hotel, bars, icecream parlour where you can grab what you prefer then just sit and relax. There use to be events keep on happening at this place. One thing if you are a dog lover you will definitely see some fashioned dogs brought by their owners. I use to go at this quite often to get myself relax 😊
Nice walking mall. Very good atmosphere. Highly recommended !
A modern and beautiful avenue. Shops were beautiful. There is a new MTR entrance in the avenue with shops on both sides of the entrance corridor.

A colourful and recent addition to Wan Chai. Many restaurants at higher prices. A below ground supermarket for those with cash to burn. Great if there's an entertainer about, but otherwise keep moving through - there's more and better to be had in Wan Chai.

result.name: 樂拉麵

reviews.text: 食品味道可以，氣氛也好。

這裡的拉麵口味, 客人可以因應自己的喜愛選擇, 麵質的軟硬程度和要唔要蒽花.

我試了特濃櫻花蝦蝦湯叉燒拉麵. 賣相精緻.除了义燒外, 當然有我最愛食的溏心蛋.配料有蓮藕, 木耳和海帶.

第一時間試了個湯底.湯底夠濃郁, 入口有蝦的味道, 加上伴有櫻花蝦, 多一份口感.溏心蛋整得剛剛好, 啱我口味.义燒偏向瘦身, 但又唔會覺得乾和硬.而我選了軟身麵質, 所以合我心意.

小食選了枝豆, 估唔到枝豆的份量也不少.

最後, 點多了一杯抹茶雪糕.雪糕質感幾幼滑, 而且抹茶味道幾香濃.
價錢和食品味道都可以。

それぞれの星の数は。。。
スープ 3
麺 1
チャーシュー 1
木耳 1
味玉 2
で、総合評価は2つ星

最近オープンする日本のラーメン屋が100ドル超えが当たり前になってる中、香港人経営とは言え80ドル以下でラーメンを提供するのは偉い。

日本で修行したと言うだけあって、スープはまあまあ。でも麺が酷すぎる。コシが全くない。さらにチャーシューは不味く、木耳も全く美味しくない。

近所に神虎麺商店があり、日本クオリティの具材を出してくれる。少々お高いが、不味くて残すくらいなら、そっちを選んでしまう。

一番大事なスープがまあまあなので、何とか改善を期待したい。

Not sure why so many one star reviews were given. 
This place has one of the best ramens I've ever had. 
It's definitely not THE best, but it's still really good. 

P.S. The sakura shrimp ramen is amazing!
